  "title": "BIM Modeller, M&E",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Design &amp; drafting of MEP layout, section details, space management planning and plant room details.</li>\n  <li>Able to carry out detailing &amp; co-ordination drawing.</li>\n  <li>Responsible for preparation of shop drawings, and As-Built drawings using Revit and CAD software.</li>\n  <li>Obtain relevant information from architectural drawings, structural, other discipline drawings.</li>\n  <li>To assist Project Manager/ Engineers on coordination, planning and visiting job sites/meetings when necessary.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma/NITEC in Engineering, Architecture or related studies</li>\n  <li>At least 3-5 years of working experiences in BIM functions (ideally from M&amp;E Trade/Discipline)</li>\n  <li>Essential to be skilled in Mechanical, Electrical or M&amp;E discipline</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If the role resonates with you and your professional experience complements the responsibilities listed, send your resume to koh.dickson@bayesrecruitment.com</p>\n<p>Dickson Koh | EA Registration R1103367</p>\n<p>bayesrecruitment.com</p>",
